About this item

  • ⌚Automatic slef-Wind Watch:Imported automatic movement, with small error, can work stably for 10 years. The sports watch through the wrist will automatically self-winding.no battery.
  • ⌚Multifunctional Dial Design:OLEVS meticulously designed 4 calendar functions of year/month/week/day to meet all customer needs, a multi-function watch with multiple times.The classic bottom moon phase window is a classic watch for gentleman men.
  • ⌚Luxury 316L Stainless Steel Strap:Solid stainless steel watch bracelet, hidden butterfly pushed button, ventilate, prevent perspiration, quality assurance.Two adjustment tools are provided to easily adjust the strap length.
  • ⌚30ATM Waterproof:Three-degree nano-level sealed waterproof, ultra-high waterproof performance, innovative and enhanced anti-fog, 30 meters strong pressure waterproof,suitable for everyday life waterproofing, such as washing hands, doing housework, and briefly soaking in water.
  • ⌚OLEVS Warranty Service:We provide 30 days free returns,2 years product high-quality assurance for the automatic watch.If you have problems during the use of the wristwatch,please feel free to contact us. We will offer you a professional service!

Product Description

Luxury mechanical self-winding mechanical watch

  • OLEVS has been involved in the watch industry for many years,the strong design and development strength, each OLEVS watch craft is designed to make you have a spiritual enjoyment that is beyond the product itself.With its own complete production chain, experienced sales team and after-sales team.
  • The watch is designed with year/month/week/date/four calendar windows to meet the needs of most people. The bottom moon phase window sets off the balance beauty of the entire dial, highlighting the personalized charm of the watch, and can be worn on various occasions.It is the innovation of OLEVS watch.

  • OLEVS has opened up the world‘s major markets in 2013, including: China, the United States, Japan, Malaysia, the United Kingdom, Gemmany, Canada, Australia, Russia,India, Indonesia and other countries in the world, and has gained a good reputation.Has become a popular intemational watch brand!
